        "content": "<p>Is it hard to allow lemmas created by <code>alias</code> to be <code>protected</code>? <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"110049\">@Mario Carneiro</span>  <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"110043\">@Gabriel Ebner</span></p>",
