    {
        "content": "<p>We could also add a <code>@[protected]</code> attribute to make it easier to set the protected flag manually.</p>",
        "id": 322645263,
        "sender_full_name": "Gabriel Ebner",
        "timestamp": 1674262486
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Is there a structural reason we can't have <code>protected</code> as an attribute?</p>",
