        "sender_full_name": "Mario Carneiro",
        "timestamp": 1674263244
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>No there's no reason at all.  We can make <code>protected</code> an attribute today.</p>",
        "id": 322646882,
        "sender_full_name": "Gabriel Ebner",
        "timestamp": 1674263473
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>can we eliminate <code>protected</code>-the-modifier?</p>",
